            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Je connais, Madame, un bonhomme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Qui serait bien mal à la Cour.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Je ne sais comment il se nomme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Sa femme n’est pas laide, en somme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Non…, elle est très digne d’amour.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je connais, Madame, un bonhomme\nQui serait bien mal à la Cour.\nJe ne sais comment il se nomme,\nSa femme n’est pas laide, en somme,\nNon…, elle est très digne d’amour."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Elle a de l’œil et de la taille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Un petit soulier de satin.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "C’est une blonde, toute en paille.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Mais, voyez, Madame, elle baille",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Dès les onze heures du matin.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Elle a de l’œil et de la taille,\nUn petit soulier de satin.\nC’est une blonde, toute en paille.\nMais, voyez, Madame, elle baille\nDès les onze heures du matin."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "L’hiver, sa servante auprès d’elle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Elle garde le coin du feu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Demandant s’il vente ou s’il gèle ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Quelquefois un bout de querelle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Avec son chéri, c’est fort peu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "L’hiver, sa servante auprès d’elle,\nElle garde le coin du feu,\nDemandant s’il vente ou s’il gèle ;\nQuelquefois un bout de querelle\nAvec son chéri, c’est fort peu."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Au mois de juin, pour la distraire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Celui-ci la mène à la mer,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Mais son fauteuil est solitaire ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Surtout, pas de célibataire ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Car ces messieurs vous ont un air…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Au mois de juin, pour la distraire,\nCelui-ci la mène à la mer,\nMais son fauteuil est solitaire ;\nSurtout, pas de célibataire ;\nCar ces messieurs vous ont un air…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Les Français, coureurs d’aventures,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Les Gaulois aux propos soignés,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Les amis de toutes natures,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Et les cousins, même en peintures,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Sont soigneusement éloignés.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les Français, coureurs d’aventures,\nLes Gaulois aux propos soignés,\nLes amis de toutes natures,\nEt les cousins, même en peintures,\nSont soigneusement éloignés."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "C’est pour des voisines posées,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Ou le regard des inconnus,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Que ses robes se sont usées ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Pas de romans, ni de musée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Où l’on voit des hommes tout nus.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C’est pour des voisines posées,\nOu le regard des inconnus,\nQue ses robes se sont usées ;\nPas de romans, ni de musée\nOù l’on voit des hommes tout nus."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "De loin en loin, les jours de foire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Une soirée avec du thé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Une valse en robe de moire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Ou la loge perdue et noire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "D’un théâtre collet monté.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "De loin en loin, les jours de foire,\nUne soirée avec du thé,\nUne valse en robe de moire,\nOu la loge perdue et noire,\nD’un théâtre collet monté."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Lorsque par hasard, elle cause",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Avec quelqu’un, c’est plus banal",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Que le papillon et la rose,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "C’est froid, c’est triste, quelque chose",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Comme les murs d’un tribunal.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Lorsque par hasard, elle cause\nAvec quelqu’un, c’est plus banal\nQue le papillon et la rose,\nC’est froid, c’est triste, quelque chose\nComme les murs d’un tribunal."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Pourtant, elle aimerait à rire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "À plaire, à plaisanter un brin,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Elle est française, c’est tout dire ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Si son cœur a ce qu’il désire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Son âme, elle, a bien du chagrin.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pourtant, elle aimerait à rire,\nÀ plaire, à plaisanter un brin,\nElle est française, c’est tout dire ;\nSi son cœur a ce qu’il désire\nSon âme, elle, a bien du chagrin."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Près de la porte de sa dame",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Le Monsieur se tient de planton ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Qu’en espère-t-il sur mon âme ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "A-t-il peur qu’on viole sa femme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Comme une poupée en carton ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Près de la porte de sa dame\nLe Monsieur se tient de planton ;\nQu’en espère-t-il sur mon âme ?\nA-t-il peur qu’on viole sa femme\nComme une poupée en carton ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Saints du Ciel, venez à leur aide",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Et qu’à l’heure où l’on fait l’amour,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Elle lui dise froide et raide :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Vois, ami, comme je suis laide,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Personne ne me fait la cour.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Saints du Ciel, venez à leur aide\nEt qu’à l’heure où l’on fait l’amour,\nElle lui dise froide et raide :\nVois, ami, comme je suis laide,\nPersonne ne me fait la cour."
        }
